jQuery Chainvas - Chainable Canvas
by James Daniels <james@jamesdaniels.net>

A quick little dirty helper to let you do things like:

$('#tutorial').getContext('2d')
  .clearRect(0,0,600,600)
  .save()
    .beginPath()
    .moveTo(200,200)
    .lineTo(0,0)
    .lineWidth(5)
    .stroke()
  .restore();

